<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-25 02:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2344 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GLF-GOLFNOTEBOOK-BOS &LR;      04-25 1645
