<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-25 03:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2365 &Cx1f; tic-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OUT-ARIZONA-BURKHART-     04-25 0655
